# Quick Start

- Read `AGENTS.md` for repo structure, workflows, and critical DON'T rules.
- Bookmark: `.devcontainer/README.md`, `docs/developer/architecture.md`, `docs/user/troubleshooting.md`.
- Core commands:
  ```bash
  ha addons logs local_cync-controller --follow
  npm run lint:python:fix && npm run format        # after any edit
  npm run lint                                     # final check
  cd cync-controller && ./rebuild.sh               # whenever Python changes
  ```
- Workflow: edit → lint & fix → rebuild (if Python) / restart (if config) → verify logs → let user commit.
- Never hardcode credentials or skip lint/rebuild requirements.
